## Komodo Environment Variables
## Copy to .env and fill in real values. NEVER commit .env.

## Shared secret between Core and all Periphery agents
KOMODO_PASSKEY=change-me-to-a-strong-random-string

## Initial admin account (only used on first launch)
KOMODO_ADMIN_USER=admin
KOMODO_ADMIN_PASS=change-me-to-a-strong-password

## Mac's Tailscale IP (run: tailscale ip -4)
MAC_TAILSCALE_IP=100.x.x.x
